This paper is likely to belong to the Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) sub-category as it focuses on the behavior of users of a health and fitness app. The paper also involves data analysis, which could place it in the Cybernetics (cs.CY) or Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper could be categorized under Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) or Computation and Language (cs.CC) as it involves analyzing text data from food journals.
